  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The name <b>Lanna</b> can refer to the following characters:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lanna_(Happy_Port)\" title=\"Lanna (Happy Port)\">Lanna</a>, a young prostitute at the Happy Port in Braavos</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lanna_(Peach)\" title=\"Lanna (Peach)\">Lanna</a>, a prostitute serving at the Peach in the Riverlands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lanna_Lannister\" title=\"Lanna Lannister\">Lanna Lannister</a>, the daughter of Ser Damion Lannister and Shiera Crakehall, and the wife of Lord Antario Jast</li></ul>\n<ul><li>Lanna Graceford (possibly), the unborn child of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Alyce_Graceford\" title=\"Alyce Graceford\">Alyce Graceford</a>, should it be a girl</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403175123\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14503-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403175123 and revision id 323447\n -->\n",
